1
00:00:00,474 --> 00:00:03,240
Well, you're more handsome in person than
in your photo.

2
00:00:03,430 --> 00:00:04,430
Welcome to Inaba.

3
00:00:05,039 --> 00:00:06,400
I'm Ryotaro Dojima.

4
00:00:06,989 --> 00:00:08,029
I'll be looking after you.

5
00:00:08,090 --> 00:00:11,540
Let's see, I'm your mother's younger
brother, and that about sums it up.

6
00:00:17,690 --> 00:00:19,800
You probably don't remember, but we've
met.

7
00:00:20,380 --> 00:00:22,160
I've changed your diapers before,
you know.

8
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:26,120
This here's my daughter.

9
00:00:26,290 --> 00:00:27,290
Come on, Nanako.

10
00:00:27,580 --> 00:00:29,000
Introduce yourself to your cousin.

11
00:00:29,854 --> 00:00:30,854
Hello?

12
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:36,360
What are you so shy for?

13
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:38,160
Ow!

14
00:00:42,555 --> 00:00:44,840
Well then, let's get going.

15
00:00:45,319 --> 00:00:46,340
My car's over there.

